[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'going to create every piece step-by-step. So, focus in, close all your open tabs, and let\'s build. So, in order to access Higgs Field, just come over to higgsfield.ai, and this is the site, and you can literally access any image and video model from right here.'

