[01:16] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'so, the last thing I\'m going to do before we get started is I took a picture of this product. It\'s just a lens cleaner for my glasses. It is not a sexy product cuz I figured if we can make a product like this look awesome, we can pretty much do it with anything. So, I\'m just going to take this image,'

